    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>这是一款2D风格的角色扮演游戏，采用即时制战斗的方式。</u></strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >关于成长的热血故事</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为了人族不再受到压迫，不再受到奴役，举起你手中的战剑，斩碎那些神的高傲！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与你的族人一起，举起大旗，为人族的未来杀出一条道路，哪怕这条道路上充满了痛苦与艰辛。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239080/extras/065db9a7174d657fc5b9497aeeaed7b2.poster.avif?t=1747039489\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239080/extras/065db9a7174d657fc5b9497aeeaed7b2.webm?t=1747039489\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239080/extras/065db9a7174d657fc5b9497aeeaed7b2.mp4?t=1747039489\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >以一敌百的战斗</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当你化身为人族最后的希望时，是否能在战斗中以一敌百，斩杀众多来犯之敌？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你手中的剑，将作为人族前进的希望，你施展的每一个魔法，都将打出更加光明的未来。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239080/extras/cac6a84b17370b149eb58a86eb5e20cd.poster.avif?t=1747039489\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239080/extras/cac6a84b17370b149eb58a86eb5e20cd.webm?t=1747039489\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239080/extras/cac6a84b17370b149eb58a86eb5e20cd.mp4?t=1747039489\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >挑战强力的敌人</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >敌人中不仅有普通的敌人，更有强力的家伙，要小心它们的攻击。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239080/extras/c11507a8acbed57c6a9e33480b5367a8.poster.avif?t=1747039489\" width=426 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239080/extras/c11507a8acbed57c6a9e33480b5367a8.webm?t=1747039489\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3239080/extras/c11507a8acbed57c6a9e33480b5367a8.mp4?t=1747039489\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >世界的帝王</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >也许一开始，你只是一个从弱小村庄中走出的少年，但随着故事的发展，你将会成为人族的领袖，直至成为帝王，你将带领你的子民们横扫大陆，成为这个世界唯一的帝王。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
